title: India : number of internet users 2015 to 2023
yAxis: Number of internet users in millions
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of internet users in millions. In total the number of data points it has is 9.
Overall Number of internet users in millions has increased over the Year.
Number of internet users in millions is slightly increasing from 2015 to 2018, and lastly roughly constant from 2018 to 2023.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
Maximum Number of internet users in millions, about 666.4 was reported at Year 2023
The lowest Number of internet users in millions, of value 259.88 was reported at Year 2015
